I got 99 cooking in late 2011 and it cost me around 15m. You could always do woodcutting (which gives you money), but it takes a long time. You won’t be able to get good XP and money at the same time (ivy has good XP but no money other than bird nests while yew/magic trees take a while to get logs and XP depending on your level).
